title: Independent candidate Mujeeb Ahmed wins PP-221 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 09 (APP): Mujeeb Ahmed, an independent candidate, has won the Punjab Assembly election from PP-221 Multan-IX by securing 15,921 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Rao Shabbir, an independent candidate, who bagged 2,262 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turnout remained 52.68 percent.
